------------WorkWork--------------- 

Description:
	A Firefox addon for a better workflow.
	
countLinks module:
    Counts the links, opened in a new tab from a site and blocks after N opened, for some time T.
	
Pomodoro module:
	http://www.pomodorotechnique.com/
	
	or more simply explained
	
	while(workTime){
		for(int i = 0; i < 4; ++i){ 
			work(25); //minutes
			break(5); //minutes
		}
		break(25); // minutes
	}

sortWork module:
	Not yet implemented.

Git repository:
	https://github.com/DuMuT6p/WorkWork
	
Credits:
	The Pomodoro Technique is a time management method developed by Francesco Cirillo in the late 1980s. 
	All rights for it belong to him.

	alarm_beep.wav is downloaded from wavsource.com and the copyrights belong to it`s owner.

